A solemn vintage-style illustration of an empty university lecture hall with rows of wooden desks and chairs, morning light streaming through tall arched windows casting long shadows across the worn floor. A single wilted flower lies abandoned on one of the front desks. The color palette is muted sepia and dusty browns with touches of faded blue, evoking 1970s editorial photography. The atmosphere is heavy with absence and stillness, dust particles visible in the light beams.
